# Group 個人機能
/api/v2/user/*


## 財布 [/api/v2/user/wallets]
Resource of Bank Account

### 財布取得 [GET]

+ Request 財布取得 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [access_token]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            {
                "wallets": [
                  {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "お財布A",
                    "amount": 100,
                    "goals": [
                      {
                        "current_amount": 0,
                        "name": "結婚式"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
            }

### 財布登録 [POST /api/v2/user/wallets/:id]

+ Request 財布登録 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [access_token]

    + Body
            {
             "wallets": {
               "name": "お財布A",
               "balance": 100
             }
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            {}

### 財布更新 [PUT /api/v2/user/wallets/:id]

+ Request 財布更新 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [access_token]

    + Body
            {
             "wallets": {
              "name":"お財布A",
              "share": true
             }
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
            {}

### 財布削除 [DELETE /api/v2/user/wallets/:id]

+ Request 財布削除 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [access_token]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {}

